{"id":"basic-arithmetic","files":[{"path":"ATTRIBUTION.md","encoding":"utf8","data":"# Image and research attribution\n\nChinese abacus, Wikimedia Commons Special:FilePath. Remote image used for educational context.\n\nEach lesson uses a distinct remote image and includes a research source link in its notes. The\nremote images are not redistributed in this source package; the reader displays them when connected\nand preserves the local SVG cover offline. Verify current reuse details at each linked Wikimedia\nCommons file page before commercial redistribution.\n\n- **Reading Numbers** — image:\n  https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Chinese_abacus.jpg; research source:\n  https://www.nctm.org/Standards-and-Positions/Principles-and-Standards/Number-and-Operations/\n- **Estimating First** — image:\n  https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Napier%27s_bones.jpg; research source:\n  https://www.nctm.org/Standards-and-Positions/Principles-and-Standards/Number-and-Operations/\n- **Addition as Combining** — image:\n  https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Counting_board.jpg; research source:\n  https://www.nctm.org/Standards-and-Positions/Principles-and-Standards/Number-and-Operations/\n- **Subtraction as Difference** — image:\n  https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Abacus_2.jpg; research source:\n  https://www.nctm.org/Standards-and-Positions/Principles-and-Standards/Number-and-Operations/\n- **Multiplication as Equal Groups** — image:\n  https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Multiplication_table_0_to_12.jpg; research\n  source:\n  https://www.nctm.org/Standards-and-Positions/Principles-and-Standards/Number-and-Operations/\n- **Division as Sharing** — image:\n  https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Division_by_sharing.svg; research source:\n  https://www.nctm.org/Standards-and-Positions/Principles-and-Standards/Number-and-Operations/\n"},{"path":"assets/images/cover.svg","encoding":"utf8","d